  "system": {
    "description": "Discipline: None\nSkill: Meditation against TN 6 (+1 for every thousand pounds)\nType: Normal\nQi: 12\n\nYou concentrate on a person or object and lift it into the air with your mind. Make a Meditation Roll against TN 6 (add +1 to the TN for every 1000 pounds). If you succeed you cause the person or object to float 10 feet per rank of Qi. In some cases, a being that is being moved by this technique may have some means of resisting (such as the Perfect Flight ability or by grabbing onto a very large and very strong object nearby). Use an Opposed roll where needed to resolve such cases. In most cases, the being that is being moved will suffer a -1d10 modifier to their roll or higher due to the terrible force exerted by this technique.",
